com.poesys.db.pk
Class MessageKeyFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.poesys.db.pk.MessageKeyFactory

public class MessageKeyFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a factory that transforms a messaging DTO into a Poesys/DB primary key (IPrimaryKey). The single getKey() method uses instanceof to detect the concrete type and produces a concrete primary key using the appropriate data from the incoming message DTO.

Author:
Robert J. Muller
